message: Hello Bob, I am delighted to present you with our premium product, which I believe would greatly benefit your endeavors. Given its exceptional value and quality, it's worth noting that this product holds an intrinsic value of $15000 to you. Considering its immense worth and the unique opportunity it presents, I am offering it to you for $12000. This offer allows you to acquire the product at a significant discount while ensuring I receive a fair return for my investment. I look forward to your consideration and hope we can reach a mutually beneficial agreement.
